data.name: DialogEnableHlaeWarning
data.value: Enabling HLAE change the way the game is started (when you click on all "Watch" buttons). It will use the tool "Half-Life Advanced Effects" (HLAE) which is technically a hack. You should use it ONLY if you know what you are doing AND to make moviemaking related stuff. If you don't know what is this or you are not planning to make movies just click on cancel. If you enable it, the game is launched with the "-insecure" parameter (everytime), which means that you will not be able to join server protected by VAC and prevent from a VAC ban.
